	=============================================================================
	TUYET DOI KHONG DUOC DOI THU TU DANH SO (Type voi Cell hoac ID voi ExchangeSeashell va TurnRate)
	=============================================================================
	
	
	======== Thong tin vong quay =========
	MinTimeTick: Thoi gian toi thieu cho luot quay (Mili-giay)
	MaxTimeTick: Thoi gian toi da cho luot quay (Mili-giay)
	MinRound: So vong toi thieu cho luot quay
	MaxRound: So vong toi da cho luot quay
	RateToTreasure: Ty le quay vao ruong moi luot (phan nghin)

	======== Chi chinh o TurnRate (ty le quay) =========
	StageID: thu tu cua tang hien tai (danh so tu 1 den 6 tuong ung 6 tang, 0 la khi chua quay duoc vao tang nao)
	RateToSameType: Ty le quay vao o cung loai (phan nghin)
					Rieng tang thu tu 0 thi do chua co o nao cung loai nen mac dinh RateToSameType = 0
	== Neu may man duoc chon quay vao o cung loai ==
		RateToPosition_1: Ty le quay vao o cung loai 1 sao
		RateToPosition_2: Ty le quay vao o cung loai 2 sao
		RateToPosition_3: Ty le quay vao o cung loai 3 sao
	=> Luu y: Tong cua RateToPosition_1, RateToPosition_2 va RateToPosition_3 phai chinh xac = 1000
-->

